    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hidden Oddities is a cosy hidden object game where you search in the nook and crannies across lush miniature landscapes, it's amazing what you might find in some of the oddest of places.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A list of items shows you what you're look at, hover over them for a closer look, and find enough to progress to the next location.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021110/extras/895eed479aa1b6ebcbc359e5f35e56d8.poster.avif?t=1728920906\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021110/extras/895eed479aa1b6ebcbc359e5f35e56d8.webm?t=1728920906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021110/extras/895eed479aa1b6ebcbc359e5f35e56d8.mp4?t=1728920906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As this game is currently in development so please keep in mind that not everything you see is the final and is subject to changes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021110/extras/bb336c8bb83266e7b5d1d06ffc8dc2b7.poster.avif?t=1728920906\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021110/extras/bb336c8bb83266e7b5d1d06ffc8dc2b7.webm?t=1728920906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021110/extras/bb336c8bb83266e7b5d1d06ffc8dc2b7.mp4?t=1728920906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Game Features so far</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 20 Levels and counting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 87+ items to find</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Non intrusive background music to relax to</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming gameplay with interactive elements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great for all ages!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021110/extras/556f7a07e2436178ea9fc59df5a24347.poster.avif?t=1728920906\" width=800 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021110/extras/556f7a07e2436178ea9fc59df5a24347.webm?t=1728920906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021110/extras/556f7a07e2436178ea9fc59df5a24347.mp4?t=1728920906\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
